premise_source_doc_sentence: Augusto José Ramón Pinochet Ugarte  (  -LSB- auˈɣusto pinoˈ  (  t  )  ʃe -RSB- or -LSB- - ˈ  (  t  )  ʃet -RSB- 25 November 1915 -- 10 December 2006  )  was a Chilean general , politician and the military ruler of Chile between 1973 and 1990 ; he remained the Commander-in-Chief of the Chilean Army until 1998 .
